Insider Activity


Individual




Leonard J. LeBlanc



Mr. Leonard J. LeBlanc is Independent Director at AXT, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at AXT, Inc.
Mr. LeBlanc was previously employed as Acting CFO & Vice President-Corporate Development by eBest!, Inc., Chairman by Oplink Communications, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by The Vantive Corp., CFO, EVP-Finance & Administration by Infoseek Corp., Senior Vice President-Finance & Administration by GTECH Corp., and CFO, Executive VP-Finance & Administration by Cadence Design Systems, Inc. He also served on the board at Optical Communication Products, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from the College of the Holy Cross (Massachusetts), a graduate degree from the College of the Holy Cross (Massachusetts), and a graduate degree from George Washington University.



