Leonard J. LeBlanc

Age : 76Public asset : 1,003,027 USDLinked companies :  AXT Inc 





Summary 



Mr. Leonard J. LeBlanc is on the Board of Directors at AXT, Inc. Mr. LeBlanc was previously employed as CFO & Vice President-Corporate Development by eBest!, Inc., Chairman by Oplink Communications LLC, Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by The Vantive Corp., CFO, Executive VP-Finance & Administration by Infoseek Corp., Senior Vice President-Finance & Administration by GTECH Corp., and CFO, Executive VP-Finance & Administration by Cadence Design Systems, Inc.He also served on the board at Optical Communication Products, Inc.He received his undergraduate degree from the College of the Holy Cross (Massachusetts), a graduate degree from the College of the Holy Cross (Massachusetts) and a graduate degree from George Washington University.



